1145
00:59:05,209 --> 00:59:06,460
[man] We're live in three, two…

1146
00:59:06,543 --> 00:59:09,296
[announcer] <i>Welcome to </i>Larry King Live!

1147
00:59:09,922 --> 00:59:11,006
