1154
00:59:23,852 --> 00:59:25,354
<i>Jack Smurl says that a demon</i>

1155
00:59:25,437 --> 00:59:27,273
<i>assaulted him in the middle of the night,</i>

1156
00:59:27,356 --> 00:59:28,857
